Description: The menstrualcycleR package provides tools for Phase-Aligned Cycle Time Scaling (PACTS),
    enabling precise and dynamic analysis of menstrual cycle data by standardizing events across
    cycles onto a continuous timeline while accounting for variability in ovulation timing and
    cycle lengths.
